the neverending story ii : the next chapter is a 1990 german-american fantasy film and sequel to the neverending story . it was directed by george t. miller and stars jonathan &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; as &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , kenny morrison as &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , and alexandra &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; as the childlike empress . the only actor to return from the first film was thomas hill as mr. &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film used plot elements from michael ende 's novel the neverending story ( primarily the second half ) but introduced a new storyline . upon its american theatrical release in 1991 , the bugs bunny animated short " box-office bunny " was shown before the film . this short was also included on the vhs and laserdisc release later that year .